{"tid":1494690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提防左膠， 瓦解初心。","createTime":"2019-08-21T17:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:42:39.000Z","uid":140246,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e52eede698422a12145b58ebadaba24d4734c58a","tid":1494690,"uid":140246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"聞到浸左膠除， 所以講下。 <br />\n<br />\n1.鬼掩眼運動 （慘劇戲謔）<br />\n2 . 何姓膠人國際talk ( 代言即icon， 大台， 光環收割， 同河童某外報被封代理人<br />\n3. 林鄭大台 （ 公子獻頭，請君入局，同當年學聯）<br />\n4. 和理勇武分化 （ 掣造矛盾對立）<br />\n5. 民陣170， 階段勝利，開會,無人駕駛，民眾分享（ 左膠絕活 - 唱k打j 宇宙大會)<br />\n6. 錢 （ 因財失義， 612基金， 星火，互損cap水 等） <br />\n7. 民間記者會大台化 （ 持份越多分裂越大） <br />\n8. 泛民主派白鴿眾（ 唔駛講都明啦）<br />\n<br />\n諗住禁多先。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得， 最緊要係人。同埋要嚴肅， 正經對待。 <br />\n此為正名。 因為膠最想化左件事。 <br />\n<br />\n一經瓦解，即退無死所。 <br />\n共勉。"},{"pid":"24509b52c29d2aad6f903ee13149ec3d173bd260","tid":1494690,"uid":27146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"你自己咪分化撚"},{"pid":"4b2c9045737e40ff2f25df227ea00dbd361e6143","tid":1494690,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:48:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主分化撚</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f38e8d9062da71b62795214946e36b86cb1bf5b1","tid":1494690,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦，你邊位呀 on9"},{"pid":"6c90d3093ac595c4991617941977d37485164e24","tid":1494690,"uid":177945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92272a888a388d30823ccaff0524c659aaf7b277","tid":1494690,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:42:39.000Z","msg":"家陣你最分化喎"}]}